Package: ShinyQuiz
Title: Framework for Collecting Data from Users in Shiny Applications
Version: 0.9.0
Date: 2022-07-18
Authors@R: 
    person("Jason", "Bryer", , "jason@bryer.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: ShinyQuiz provides a framework for collecting data from users
    through a series of questions. Common uses include short multiple
    choice quizzes, survey questions, or essays. The package supports
    responses as radio buttons (with one selection allowed), check boxes
    (allowoing for multiple answers per question), numeric responses, and
    text boxes.
License: GPL-3
